[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "beardist"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2024"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "beardist"
edition = "2024"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["Amos Wenger <amos@bearcove.eu>"]
description = "Builds Rust code in CI and uploads it to GitHub Releases / registry"
keywords = ["distribution", "tool"]
categories = ["command-line-utilities"]
license = "Apache-2.0/MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/bearcove/beardist"

[dependencies]
camino = "1.1.9"
color-eyre = "0.6.3"
convert_case = "0.8.0"

fs-err = "3.1.0"
glob = "0.3.2"
hostname = "0.4.1"

log = "0.4.27"
owo-colors = "4.2.0"
rand = "0.9.1"
regex = "1.11.1"
semver = "1.0.26"
serde_json = "1.0.140"
sha2 = "0.10.8"
sys-info = "0.9.1"
tempfile = "3.19.1"
url = "2.5.4"

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.5.37"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.12.15"
features = ["blocking", "json"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.219"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.timelord]
version = "3.0.2"

[dev-dependencies]
tempfile = "3.19.1"
